<H1>Display system name</H1>

<P>To display the name of the system in the prompt:</P>

<P><STRONG>1.</STRONG> Use your editor to open your <SAMP>.kshrc</SAMP>
 file and add the line:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   PS1='$HOST $'
</PRE>

<P><STRONG>2.</STRONG> Save the file and leave the editor.</P>

<P><STRONG>3.</STRONG> Enter the command:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>. .kshrc</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>This adds the new values to your working environment.</P>

